        "body": "The live wallpaper feature is not working on the macOS lock screen. While the application works correctly on the desktop, the wallpaper does not appear or play when the system is locked.\n\nSteps to Reproduce\nInstall and open the app on macOS\nApply any live wallpaper\nLock the screen (Ctrl + Cmd + Q or wait for auto-lock)\nObserve the lock screen\nExpected Behavior\n\nThe live wallpaper should continue to display and play on the macOS lock screen, similar to how it works on the desktop.\nActual Behavior\nThe lock screen either shows a static wallpaper or no live wallpaper at all.\nIf this is a limitation due to macOS restrictions, it would be helpful to clarify in the documentation. Otherwise, support for lock screen live wallpapers would be a great feature.",
